393
00:40:15.758 --> 00:40:17.484
I followed.

394
00:40:17.518 --> 00:40:19.244
And I am so proud

395
00:40:19.278 --> 00:40:21.591
to have worked for the man
all these long years.

396
00:40:26.769 --> 00:40:27.873
When I lost my w...

397
